| -------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| âœ… Need private access to AWS service (like S3, KMS, Secrets Manager) | âœ… Yes            | Keeps all traffic inside AWS â€” avoids NAT/internet |
