ğŸ’° Pricing Considerations
Per-hour charge for each interface endpoint (ENI)

Data processed (GB) through the endpoint

Pricing varies per region, but typically includes:

Interface endpoint hourly cost

Per GB data processing

No charges for DNS or route table changes

